					TODO: Prohibited activities, security expectations, and compliance requirements.
				</p>
			</section>

		<section class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-slate-900/40 shadow-sm p-6">
			<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Disclaimers and limitation of liability</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
					TODO: Standard B2B disclaimers and liability caps (counsel-reviewed).
				</p>
			</section>

		<section class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-slate-900/40 shadow-sm p-6">
			<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">Termination</h2>
